SR NO. 46 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby designate Wednesday, April 1, 2026, as Professional Landscape Architecture
Day at the Louisiana State Capitol and does commend the members for the essential role
landscape architects play in shaping a resilient and enduring American landscape.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
president of the Louisiana Chapter of the American Society of Landscape Architects.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
